{"tid":960483,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人已經唔知許咩生日願望好？","createTime":"2018-12-29T12:41:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-29T13:20:02.000Z","uid":11293,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c181e6cefbb7ed6c110fffe0c973e4148875e9af","tid":960483,"uid":11293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T12:41:19.000Z","msg":"話說今日小弟生日<br />\n朋友買咗個蛋糕同我慶祝生日，例牌有生日蛋糕同唱生日歌，但係到我許生日願望嘅時候，真係唔知許咩好<br />\n所以最後我合手合眼兩秒就吹熄枝蠟燭<br />\n有無人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52c9003916cc18a7711918d796fac2e709f24012","tid":960483,"uid":107364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T12:44:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"30236970a6fc1d8fc84e45ab2891ac2133071280","tid":960483,"uid":59536,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"52c9003916cc18a7711918d796fac2e709f24012","tid":960483,"uid":107364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T12:44:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T12:44:54.000Z","msg":"祝你許願成真<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b272965af4cb11e941206dd7563c09b7260e6909","tid":960483,"uid":93655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T12:45:08.000Z","msg":"我尋日生日都係咁<br />\n俾人問有咩生日願望果時口啞啞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw生日快樂"},{"pid":"23949e22511fb45c3ffb84a23cdd0f4f08b63f43","tid":960483,"uid":3501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T13:18:33.000Z","msg":"細個試過許世界和平<br />\n<br />\n諗返起打左個冷震<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e87a9051ceafbe723b5e4be6bd34ed0c06ced508","tid":960483,"uid":227471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23949e22511fb45c3ffb84a23cdd0f4f08b63f43","tid":960483,"uid":3501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T13:18:33.000Z","msg":"細個試過許世